	 <waseem.alwahedy@ku.ac.ae <mailto:waseem.alwahedy@ku.ac.ae> >\; aeldeeb@K
	pmg.Com <mailto:aeldeeb@Kpmg.Com> \nSubject: RE: Review of EHS - Draft rep
	ort & Closing meeting\n\n \n\nGood morning Dr Abdulaziz \n\nLooking forwar
	d to see you on the 10th of July \n\nMy best time will be from 10 to 11 am
	 \n\nIf OK\, please arrange to schedule a meeting in order to discuss the 
	report outcome \n\n \n\nBest Regards\, \n\n \n\nMohamed Abdulla Jasim AlHo
	sani\nDirector\, Administration and Facilities\nAdministration and Facilit
	ies\n\n\n\nP O Box 127788\, Abu Dhabi\, UAE \nKhalifa University of Scienc
	e and Technology\n\nT +971 2 312 3322 \nmohamed.alhosani@ku.ac.ae <mailto:
	mohamed.alhosani@ku.ac.ae> \n\nku.ac.ae <https://www.ku.ac.ae/> \n\n <http
	s://www.facebook.com/khalifauniversity/>  <https://twitter.com/KhalifaUni>
	  <https://www.instagram.com/khalifauniversity>  <https://www.youtube.com/
	user/khalifauniversity>  <https://www.linkedin.com/school/khalifauniversit
	y/>  <https://www.tiktok.com/@khalifauniversity?_t=8Y048LBBqpV&_r=1> \n\n\
	n\nFrom: Abdulaziz Alkhoori <abdulaziz.alkhoori@ku.ac.ae <mailto:abdulaziz
	.alkhoori@ku.ac.ae> > \nSent: Thursday\, June 22\, 2023 1:12 PM\nTo: Moham
	ed Abdulla Jasim AlHosani <mohamed.alhosani@ku.ac.ae <mailto:mohamed.alhos
	ani@ku.ac.ae> >\nCc: Anamika Menon <anamika.menon@ku.ac.ae <mailto:anamika
	.menon@ku.ac.ae> >\; Waseem Alwahedy <waseem.alwahedy@ku.ac.ae <mailto:was
	eem.alwahedy@ku.ac.ae> >\; aeldeeb@Kpmg.Com <mailto:aeldeeb@Kpmg.Com> \nSu
	bject: Review of EHS - Draft report & Closing meeting\n\n \n\nDear Mohamed
	\,\n\n \n\nHope all is well with you.\n\n \n\nI would like to thank you an
	d your team for your assistance and cooperation with Internal Audit during
	 our review of EHS. Attached is the draft report for your thoughtful revie
	w\; and as per our standard audit protocol we would like to schedule a “
	Closing Meeting” with you to discuss the report's content in more depth\
	, confirm our findings\, receive any feedback you may have\, and discuss p
	otential remedial actions or improvements.\n\n \n\nGiven that next week is
	 mostly Eid Holidays\, let’s aim to have the meeting on the week startin
	g Monday\, July 10th. This timeframe will provide your team with ample tim
	e to review the draft report and prepare for the meeting. To coordinate th
	e logistics\, please feel free to reach out to Anamika from our team.\n\n 
	\n\nThanks again & Eid Mubarak\,\n\n \n\nAbdulaziz Alkhoori\nVice Presiden
	t\, Audit\nAudit\n\n\n\nP O Box 127788\, Abu Dhabi\, UAE \nKhalifa Univers
	ity of Science and Technology\n\nT \nabdulaziz.alkhoori@ku.ac.ae <mailto:a
	bdulaziz.alkhoori@ku.ac.ae> \n\nku.ac.ae <https://www.ku.ac.ae/> \n\n <htt
	ps://www.facebook.com/khalifauniversity/>  <https://twitter.com/KhalifaUni
	>  <https://www.instagram.com/khalifauniversity>  <https://www.youtube.com
	/user/khalifauniversity>  <https://www.linkedin.com/school/khalifauniversi
	ty/>  <https://www.tiktok.com/@khalifauniversity?_t=8Y048LBBqpV&_r=1> \n\n
	\n\n \n\n
