	<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Dear Mohamed\,
	<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal
	>Hope all is well with you.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;<
	/o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>I would like to thank you and your team for yo
	ur assistance and cooperation with Internal Audit during our review of EHS
	. Attached is the draft report for your thoughtful review\; and as per our
	 standard audit protocol we would like to schedule a &#8220\;Closing Meeti
	ng&#8221\; with you to discuss the report's content in more depth\, confir
	m our findings\, receive any feedback you may have\, and discuss potential
	 remedial actions or improvements.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&
	nbsp\;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Given that next week is mostly Eid Holi
	days\, let&#8217\;s aim to have the meeting on the week starting Monday\, 
	July 10th. This timeframe will provide your team with ample time to review
	 the draft report and prepare for the meeting. To coordinate the logistics
	\, please feel free to reach out to Anamika from our team.<o:p></o:p></p><
	p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Thanks again &a
	mp\; Eid Mubarak\,<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p>
